(88, 1, 0x323031362d30352d31392031363a35353a3230, 0x323031362d30352d31392030383a35353a3230, '<div>在Z觅和J盛工作过程中遇到了不少网站，主要是一些娱乐性质或给人以想法的网站，现在整理记录下来</div>\r\n<!--more--><br clear=\"none\" /><a href=\"https://prism-break.org/zh-CN/categories/windows/\" target=\"_blank\" shape=\"rect\">https://prism-break.org/zh-CN/categories/windows/</a> 隐私软件推荐<br clear=\"none\" /><a href=\"http://user.kdnet.net/index.asp?userid=270408#post\" target=\"_blank\" shape=\"rect\">http://user.kdnet.net/index.asp?userid=270408#post</a>    东京博士<br clear=\"none\" /><a href=\"http://www.hanzify.org/software/top_%B9%D9%B7%BD%D6%D0%CE%C4.html\" target=\"_blank\" shape=\"rect\">http://www.hanzify.org/software/top_%B9%D9%B7%BD%D6%D0%CE%C4.html</a>   汉化<br clear=\"none\" /><a href=\"http://gate.sinovision.net:82/gate/big5/\" target=\"_blank\" shape=\"rect\">http://gate.sinovision.net:82/gate/big5/</a>    ..未知<a href=\"http://gate.sinovision.net:82/gate/big5/blog.sinovision.net/home/space/uid/221246/do/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" shape=\"rect\"><br clear=\"none\" />blog.sinovision.net/home/space/uid/221246/do/index.html</a>  <a href=\"http://user.sinovision.net/home/space/uid/221246.html\" target=\"_blank\" shape=\"rect\">皓易堂</a>主页<br clear=\"none\" /><a href=\"http://smartladder.googlecode.com/svn/hosts/pc/hosts\" target=\"_blank\" shape=\"rect\">http://smartladder.googlecode.com/svn/hosts/pc/hosts</a><br clear=\"none\" /><a href=\"http://i.youku.com/u/UMjY3NjM5NTE2\" target=\"_blank\" shape=\"rect\">http://i.youku.com/u/UMjY3NjM5NTE2</a>           kt无双<br clear=\"none\" /><a href=\"http://movie.douban.com/review/6506433/\" target=\"_blank\" shape=\"rect\">http://movie.douban.com/review/6506433/</a>      <span style=\"color: #000000;\"><a href=\"http://movie.douban.com/review/6506433/黄青蕉\" target=\"_blank\" shape=\"rect\">黄青蕉</a></span><br clear=\"none\" /><a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/articlelist_1197950454_0_1.html\" target=\"_blank\" shape=\"rect\">http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/articlelist_1197