(190, 1, 0x323031362d30352d31392032333a31393a3231, 0x323031362d30352d31392031353a31393a3231, '今天多看好多眼的女人\r\n今天不知道是怎么回事，多看了好多眼的女人，无论是成双的还是单个。今天我是怎么了？单身时间太长了么？', '5月19日', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '5yue19ri', '', '', 0x323031362d30362d32392030393a30323a3437, 0x323031362d30362d32392030313a30323a3437, '', 0, 'http://mxy0226.comlu.com/?p=190', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(193, 1, 0x323031362d30362d30362031313a31333a3035, 0x323031362d30362d30362030333a31333a3035, '', 'bg_dark', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'bg_dark', '', '', 0x323031362d30362d30362031313a31333a3035, 0x323031362d30362d30362030333a31333a3035, '', 0, 'http://mxy0226.comlu.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/bg_dark.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(226, 1, 0x323031362d30362d31342032323a30363a3331, 0x323031362d30362d31342031343a30363a3331, '前段时间安装了ubuntu。结果安装virtualbox时报错：是python的。结果就把python的默认版本变成3.5了，结果不仅没解决问题，每次使用python都不爽。\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n网上有说怎么改回去[http://mehuping.blog.163.com/blog/static/1366666442010822393722/]：\r\n\r\nsudo rm /usr/bin/python\r\n\r\nsudo ln -s /usr/include/python2.5 /usr/bin/python\r\n\r\n这样在终端中输入python默认就是 2.5版本了。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n第二步我这不成功，需运行\r\n\r\nsudo ln -s /usr/bin/python2.7 /usr/bin/python', 'ubuntu下的python', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ubuntu%e4%b8%8b%e7%9a%84python', '', '', 0x323031362d31302d30382031353a31333a3030, 0x323031362d31302d30382030373a31333a3030, '', 0, 'http://45.78.41.247/?p=226', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(198, 1, 0x323031362d30362d30372030383a34393a3033, 0x323031362d30362d30372030303a34393a3033, '我想做的事情是如此的多，我已经不知道有多少了，因为现在我只能想，没有做\r\n我想做什么呢？\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<del>我想每天晚上都能跑上一会</del>（时有时无）\r\n<del>我想有天能去店里买件新衣</del>（有电瓶车后到超市买过短裤）\r\n<del>我想每天晚上能早点休息</del>（时早时晚）\r\n<del>我想去买一辆电瓶车</del>(姚哥朋友)\r\n我想换一间房\r\n<del>我想去洗衣服</del>(清除计划)\r\n我想申请一张可以无国界使用的银行卡\r\n我想做网络安全工程师\r\n\r\n...', '我想', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e6%88%91%e6%83%b3', '', '', 0x323031362d31302d30382031353a32363a3032, 0x323031362d31302d30382030373a32363a3032, '', 0, 'http://mxy0226.comlu.com/?p=198', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(256, 1, 0x323031362d30362d32302030373a31333a3234, 0x323031362d30362d31392032333a31333a3234, '=========================\r\n\r\n2016/6/20\r\n\r\n每次都给自己一个最后时间，到了这个时间发现自己什么都没有完成，就想重置所有，希望大破现有，希望重来。\r\n\r\n今天没有想往常一样，而是坐到七宝站，进去买东西，以为会晚7：30汽车，结果早十分钟。在去的路上，我想如果没有风险真是太没有激情了。这时真么回事？(0621)\r\n\r\n严格来说，今天不是另一个开始。每一个开始前都会蕴酿出一个想法：把所有的负担清空掉；每个被担心的，懒散的，不可能的事，都清除掉。\r\n\r\n但是总会有一些事会慢慢的留下来。如果有可能清空掉，那会有新的未来么？\r\n\r\n那怎么才能每天都清掉？\r\n1 每天都当作是最后一天？\r\n2 是不是有些事给自己的期限在多？\r\n3 有时间把自己想做的事列出来\r\n\r\n今天就是，那下个重置是什么时候？\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', '循环：开始', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e5%be%aa%e7%8e%af%ef%bc%9a%e5%bc%80%e5%a7%8b', '', '', 0x323031362d30372d30332032323a31313a3434, 0x323031362d30372d30332031343a31313a3434, '', 0, 'http://45.78.41.247/?p=256', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(209, 1, 0x323031362d30362d31322031303a32383a3437, 0x323031362d30362d31322030323a32383a3437, '上周在单片机中添加了新的功能：添加信号图标。\r\n\r\n以下为添加的方式：\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n在LCD屏里自定义图标时，会涉及到图标的字模数据。可以使用现有工具添加：zimo22【<a href=\"http://mxy0226.comlu.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/zimo22.7z\">zimo22 </a>】\r\n\r\n使用如下[仅用图标16*16]：\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>基本操作-&gt;打开图标</li>\r\n 	<li>修改图案-&gt;修改点格颜色(将每个点格设置显示/不显示) | 改变图片大小</li>\r\n 	<li>参数设置-&gt;其它选项(设置提取方式 横向/竖向)</li>\r\n 	<li>取模方式-&gt;点击C51格式(下方即显示值)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n以下图标:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://45.78.41.247/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/sig_1.bmp\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-270\" src=\"http://45.78.41.247/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/sig_1.bmp\" alt=\"sig_1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://45.78.41.247/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/sig_2.bmp\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-271\" src=\"http://45.78.41.247/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/sig_2.bmp\" alt=\"sig_2\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://45.78.41.247/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/sig_3.bmp\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-272\" src=\"http://45.78.41.247/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/sig_3.bmp\" alt=\"sig_3\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n3格\r\n0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x0E,0x00,0x0E,0x00,0x0E,0x00,0x0E,0x01,0xCE,0x01,0xCE,\r\n0x01,0xCE,0x01,0xCE,0x39,0xCE,0x39,0xCE,0x39,0xCE,0x39,0xCE,0x39,0xCE,0x39,0xCE\r\n2格\r\n0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x01,0xC0,0x01,0xC0,\r\n0x01,0xC0,0x01,0xC0,0x39,0xC0,0x39,0xC0,0x39,0xC0,0x39,0xC0,0x39,0xC0,0x39,0xC0\r\n\r\n1格\r\n0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,\r\n0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x38,0x00,0x38,0x00,0x38,0x00,0x38,0x00,0x38,0x00,0x38,0x00\r\n\r\n以上。\r\n\r\n附显示/设置方式：图标是设置在RAM中。所以每次上电都要设置一次。\r\n\r\n/***************************************************\r\n自定义字符写入CGRAM\r\n总共有4个自定义字符\r\n写入地址    0x40   0x50   0x60   0x70\r\n对应的读出地址为    0x00   0x02   0x04   0x06\r\n****************************************************/\r\n\r\n先定义三个图标，然后将图标写入到地址0x40，0x50，0x60；\r\n显示的时候再将0x00   0x02   0x04显示到三个位置（如0x89,0x8a,0x8b）\r\n\r\n//----\r\nvoid Wr_Cgram_19264F( BYTE type) {\r\n// 三格信号\r\nBYTE sig_3[] = {\r\n0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x0E,0x00,0x0E,0x00,0x0E,0x00,0x0E,0x01,0xCE,0x01,0xCE,\r\n0x01,0xCE,0x01,0xCE,0x39,0xCE,0x39,0xCE,0x39,0xCE,0x39,0xCE,0x39,0xCE,0x39,0xCE\r\n};\r\n//两格信号\r\nBYTE sig_2[] = {\r\n0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x01,0xC0,0x01,0xC0,\r\n0x01,0xC0,0x01,0xC0,0x39,0xC0,0x39,0xC0,0x39,0xC0,0x39,0xC0,0x39,0xC0,0x39,0xC0\r\n};\r\n//一格信号\r\nBYTE sig_1[] = {\r\n0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,\r\n0x00,0x00,0x00,0x00,0x38,0x00,0x38,0x00,0x38,0x00,0x38,0x00,0x38,0x00,0x38,0x00\r\n};\r\nBYTE write_sig = 1;\r\nBYTE addr;\r\nBYTE *val;\r\n\r\nswitch (type) {\r\ncase SIG_1:\r\naddr = 0x40;\r\nval = sig_1;\r\nbreak;\r\ncase SIG_2:\r\naddr = 0x50;\r\nval = sig_2;\r\nbreak;\r\ncase SIG_3:\r\naddr = 0x60;\r\nval = sig_3;\r\nbreak;\r\ndefault:\r\nwrite_sig = 0;\r\nbreak;\r\n}\r\n\r\nif (write_sig) {\r\nfor(BYTE i=0;i&lt;16;i++) {\r\nwrite_cmd(addr+i);//设定CGRAM地址\r\nwrite_data(val[2*i]);\r\nwrite_data(val[2*i+1]);\r\n}\r\n}\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n//----\r\nvoid Disp_Cgram_19264F(BYTE type)\r\n{\r\nBYTE show_sig = 1;\r\nBYTE addr;\r\nBYTE *val;\r\n\r\nswitch (type) {\r\ncase SIG_1:\r\naddr = 0x00;\r\nbreak;\r\ncase SIG_2:\r\naddr = 0x02;\r\nbreak;\r\ncase SIG_3:\r\naddr = 0x04;\r\nbreak;\r\ndefault:\r\nshow_sig = 0;\r\nbreak;\r\n}\r\n\r\nwrite_cmd(0x8b);\r\nif (show_sig==0) {\r\nwrite_data(0x20);\r\nwrite_data(0x20);\r\n} else {\r\nwrite_data(0x00);\r\nwrite_data(addr);\r\n}\r\n}', '关于LCD屏的字模提取', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e5%85%b3%e4%ba%8elcd%e5%b1%8f%e7%9a%84%e5%ad%97%e6%a8%a1%e6%8f%90%e5%8f%96', '', '', 0x323031362d31302d30382031353a30383a3038, 0x323031362d31302d30382030373a30383a3038, '', 0, 'http://mxy0226.comlu.com/?p=209', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(210, 1, 0x323031362d30362d31322031303a31333a3532, 0x323031362d30362d31322030323a31333a3532, '', 'zimo22', '字模软件', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'zimo22', '', '', 0x323031362d30362d31322031303a31343a3037, 0x323031362d30362d31322030323a31343a3037, '', 209, 'http://mxy0226.comlu.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/zimo22.7z', 0, 'attachment', 'application/x-7z-compressed', 0),
